  22 Jun 2008; Samuli Suominen <drac@gentoo.org> +xfburn-0.3.0.ebuild:
  Move from xfce-extra. New USE flags for dbus and hal. Rename USE minimal
  to USE xfce as it will be used more in future. Marked amd64 stable.

